title: NFL Draft Chatter with Dane Brugler, NFL Mock Recap with Ryan Wilson (Football 4/19)
description:
Will Brinson and Ryan Wilson break down the live CBS Sports HQ mock draft from Thursday and then Brinson welcomes on Dane Brugler of The Athletic to talk about his giant mock draft guide and how he sees the draft playing out, plus some prospects to watch.
